{"id":588523,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/【众人推】没有共产党就没有如来佛/","date":"2018-07-09T01:27:32Z","modified":"2018-07-10T04:53:30Z","title":"【众人推】“没有共产党就没有如来佛”","content":"<p>【编者按】近日，一张来源不详的照片流传推特。照片背景是一座青灰色的石库门楼房。房门口红色遮阳方伞上写有“中共一大会址纪念馆”字样。图中一队出家女尼排行整齐，似乎在等在检票入馆参观。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_588524\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-588524\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/DhkgSoJVMAAhOfS-300x251.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"251\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/DhkgSoJVMAAhOfS-300x251.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/DhkgSoJVMAAhOfS-768x642.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/DhkgSoJVMAAhOfS-1024x856.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/DhkgSoJVMAAhOfS.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">一大会址纪念馆前的队伍<br />（图片来源于网络）</p></div>\n<p>此前，中国官媒就曾发布游客排长队参观一大会址的信息（如下图）。但这次照片主角非普通游客而是一众僧尼。出家人不礼佛，却排队膜拜共产文化遗迹，着实让人摸不着头脑。对此，艺术家华涌（@HuaYong798)发推文感叹：中国人“信仰混乱”！</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_588525\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-588525\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/LOCAL201710181503000260995921985-300x175.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"175\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/LOCAL201710181503000260995921985-300x175.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/LOCAL201710181503000260995921985-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/LOCAL201710181503000260995921985-80x48.jpg 80w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/LOCAL201710181503000260995921985.jpg 850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">参观中共一大会址纪念馆（人民网：<a href=\"http://sh.people.com.cn/n2/2017/1018/c134836-30841252.html\">http://sh.people.com.cn/n2/2017/1018/c134836-30841252.html</a>）</p></div>\n<p>网友也众说纷纭，展开了精彩热议……</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">不是他们信仰混乱。是强权之下无自由。</p>\n<p>&mdash; abenman (@abenman) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/abenman/status/1015970842289688576?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 8, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">没有共产党就没有如来佛.jpg</p>\n<p>&mdash; 文莱香客 (@lalunayb1) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lalunayb1/status/1016128802907443205?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 9, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">信仰佛教信主义，拜完观音拜主席</p>\n<p>&mdash; 云中鹤 (@alexlee19890415) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/alexlee19890415/status/1016029507365396480?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 8, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">一大會址改為寺廟了？ <a href=\"https://t.co/RSJ73H7973\">pic.twitter.com/RSJ73H7973</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 何頻 (@nyhopin) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nyhopin/status/1016008785742086144?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 8, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">僧不像僧，道不像道，只是习主席愈来愈似马克思。</p>\n<p>&mdash; 🐔炼兵🐔 (@fangli525) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/fangli525/status/1016026866472366080?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 8, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf